Uses all 13 departments.

Shows:
- Total departments
- Complete count
- Incomplete count
- Not running count
- optional completion ratio

Example:
Departments Completed
Complete: 8
Incomplete: 2
Not running: 3
Total: 13

B. Metric Summary

Uses only:
- Injection
- MetaPress
- Berks
- Wilts

Shows:
- Total downtime minutes
- Average efficiency where values exist
- Average yield where values exist
