Important:
Metric Summary must not include:
- Racking
- Butchery
- Further Processing
- Tumblers
- Smoke Tumbler
- Minimums & Samples
- Goods In & Despatch
- Dry Goods
- Additional

C. Attachment Summary

Shows:
- total attachments for session
